This package will give substantial amount of help to people who works in trading or any finance related field. 

This package interpolate with many statistical tools and unsupervised machine learning and all user friendly way. 
This specifically targets to analyze the stock market of SnP500 in US. It mainly works with closing price but with little
tweak of the function, it can get any data in OLHC informations of stocks. 

Function scrape the data from any source of financial data provider such as yahoo finance and does have visualize functioning for various reasoning.
Market risk and analysis of trend and regime are availble from functions.

All dataframe can be converted to Rdata to speed up the anlaysis if user decide to use heavy amount of datas by selecting periods of analysis.
As long as data provide(source) can give out, user can choose any valid dates or period to analyze. 
